cat("To whomever is reading this and does not reside or originate from planet Earth,\nI am a citizen of planet earth and am writing you in hopes of sparking an interaction and collaboration between\nour two great planets in the hope of bettering the lives of all who live in both. If you are willing, we would love\nto set up a meeting somewhere in space where we can discuss the interaction and/or gradual assimilation\nbetween our two planets. Please let us know you thought and we are excited about the posibility of meeting and learning\nfrom/about you all.\nRespectfully,\nErik Ross\nCitizen and Representative of of Planet Earth")
